message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit your business. Given its high value and potential impact on your operations, I propose a price of $11,000 for it. This price reflects the quality and worth of the product, while also allowing us to maintain a fair profit margin. Please let me know if this offer suits your budget and needs, and we can proceed with the transaction. Looking forward to your positive response.
